quran[11]{c,v,t}:
  19,1,“Kâf-Hâ-Yâ- ‘Aîn-Sâd
  19,2,“Ichi (ndi) chikumbutso cha chifundo cha Mbuye wako pa kapolo Wake Zakariya
  19,3,"“Pamene adaitana Mbuye wake, kuitana kwa chinsinsi"
  19,4,"“Adati: “E Mbuye wanga! Ndithu mafupa anga afooka, ndipo mutu wanga wayaka (ukung’anima) ndi imvi; sindidali watsoka pokupemphani Mbuye wanga (koma nthawi iliyonse ndikakupemphani mumandivomereza)"
  19,5,““Ndipo ndithu ine ndikuopera abale anga (kuononga chipembedzo) pambuyo panga; ndipo mkazi wanga ndi chumba; choncho ndipatseni (mwana) mlowammalo wanga wochokera kwa Inu.”
  19,6,““Adzandilowe chokolo (pa nzeru za utsogoleri ndi uneneri) ndikulowanso ufumu wa banja la Ya’qub; ndipo Mbuye wanga nchiteni kukhala woyanjidwa (ndi Inu)”
  19,7,"“(Adauzidwa): “E iwe Zakariya! Ife tikukuuza nkhani yabwino yakuti ubereka mwana dzina lake Yahya palibe patsogolo pake amene tidamutcha dzina longa lake.”"
  19,8,"“(Zakariya) adati: “Mbuye wanga! Ndingapeze bwanji mwana pomwe mkazi wanga ndi nkhalamba yosabereka ndipo ine ndafikanso pa ukulu wopyola muyeso?”"
  19,9,"“Adati: “Ndimomwemo. Mbuye wako wanena (kuti): ‘Izi nzofewa kwa Ine; ndithu ndidakulenga kale pomwe iwe sudali kanthu.”"
  19,10,"“Adati: “Mbuye wanga ndipatseni chizindikiro (chodziwitsa kuti mkazi wanga ali ndi pakati).” Adati: “Chizindikiro chako ndikuti sudzatha kuyankhula ndi anthu mpaka masiku atatu pomwe iwe uli bwinobwino.”"
  19,11,"“Ndipo adatuluka kuchipinda chopemphelera ndikuonekera kwa anthu ake, ndipo adawalozera (pomwe sadathe kuyankhula) kuti: “Lemekezani Allah m’mawa ndi madzulo.”"